name: THESINS//006 : THE LONELY HOUR PT.2
description:
“Carl hasn't been home for a week.” May told everyone. She saw them talking, muttering, but her mind was frantic, she didn’t even listen.
suddenly her phone rang. Tom's name appeared. everyone was silent and watched May.
“Yes?” Answered May hesitantly. No sound from the other side. “Tom?” May started to worry. “May.. umm. Can we meet?” Tom sounded uncomfortable. “I don’t think that’s a good idea.” Answered May, even though she misses him so much, she knew meeting Tom will only make things worse. “Please?”
She hung up her phone. And the last thing she knew, she was already at Tom’s door.
